{"tid":320862,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"這三個妹子你喜歡誰？據說選「她」的絕對是處男...網友驚：糟糕被發現了！","createTime":"2017-07-13T23:26:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-11T09:06:50.000Z","uid":1735,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"3bec62602267bfad5c61fa300dd73cbd4ee06193","tid":320862,"uid":1735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T23:26:29.000Z","msg":"最近日本2ch上又來張區分是「處男」跟「非處男」的照片啦<br />\n<br />\n不過這次比起說是處男，這次大家都在說選「她」絕對不是處男啦!!<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/14/072437_01bf4ba52f0c2c4e50531b18d0ca4614.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F14%2F072437_01bf4ba52f0c2c4e50531b18d0ca4614.jpg&h=76baadf7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n你先說如果是你會選誰<br />\n<br />\n相信大家都知道～<br />\n<br />\n多數的人會說最左邊的妹妹是處男才會選的！<br />\n<br />\n那麼非處男又會選誰呢？<br />\n<br />\n「我非處男！選中間！」<br />\n<br />\n「右邊看了就火大、左邊只是女乃大」<br />\n<br />\n「處男一定選左」<br />\n<br />\n總之林林總總加下來，非處男者都表示要選「中間」！<br />\n<br />\n不曉得你們怎麼選哩？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea642b913528d4a8150a7c1703ca7d4e01782d2e","tid":320862,"uid":105445,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T23:27:24.000Z","msg":"Why not both<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6b4698a8313321a594c0d1356ec143e2a87b22d","tid":320862,"uid":19151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T23:28:36.000Z","msg":"日本人就好，見得多大波都厭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我實揀左"},{"pid":"1cc21bfd1bdfdca8205c5c932be1a33c62d83ae4","tid":320862,"uid":3179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T23:32:23.000Z","msg":"中間果個老江湖？"},{"pid":"18bddd10637173d1ce3fe38f5c3569c25f95526d","tid":320862,"uid":53568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T23:36:38.000Z","msg":"三個我屌曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkg